column2: I love Michael Jackson. Who is Janet Marylyn Frager’s son?
column4: Answer the question as accurately and concisely as possible. Today is November 15, 2025.

column2: Janet Marylyn Frager is the mother of **Brandon Howard**, an American singer who has at times been rumored (without confirmed evidence) to be Michael Jackson’s son.
Janet Marilyn Frager (often spelled “Janet *Marilyn* Frager”) is the mother of **Mark Ronson**, the British-American musician, DJ, and producer.
Janet Marylyn Frager (better known as Janet Jackson, born Janet Damita Jo Jackson) has one son: **Eissa Al Mana**, born January 3, 2017.

Janet Marylyn Frager is better known as Janet Arvizo, the mother who accused Michael Jackson in the 2005 trial.  

Her son is **Gavin Arvizo**, the boy who alleged that Michael Jackson molested him.

Janet Marylyn Frager is better known as Janet Jackson (her full name is Janet Damita Jo Jackson; “Frager” is not part of her legal name).

Janet Jackson has one child: her son **Eissa Al Mana**, born January 3, 2017, with her then-husband Wissam Al Mana.
